<taxonomicName authorityName="Zelazny &amp; Webb" authorityYear="2011" box="[779,866,1182,1206]" class="Insecta" family="Derbidae" genus="Rhotana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="100" pageNumber="101" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mendax">
<emphasis box="[779,866,1182,1206]" italics="true" pageId="100" pageNumber="101">mendax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
= deceptive) which remains unchanged in all gen- der forms.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
